    <description>
        The Asynchronous Game Query Library (AGQL) aims to be one-stop solution for all type of game queries. It
        provides implementations covering for a wide variety of protocols by popular game vendors (e.g. Valve,
        Supercell).
        The core transport engine is powered by Netty, a powerful NIO client/server framework. That said, ALL game
        protocol interfaces within this library are asynchronous!
    </description>

